data.description: WOW! Did you see what just happened? BUYERS just got a bonus! **AGENTS, PLEASE READ REALTOR ONLY REMARKS.** The property you are inquiring about is located in Polk County, FL in the Greentree area of Lakeland. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath pool home with 2,276 square feet living is situated on a fenced lot, boasting over 1/3 of an acre with a backyard tropical paradise. Enjoy a bounty of fruit trees including avocado, jackfruit, tangerine, banana, and pineapple plants! Other amenities include new windows, fireplace, storage shed, and screened lanai. Easy access to major thoroughfares and close in shopping and medical - make your appointment today! **AGENTS, PLEASE READ REALTOR ONLY REMARKS.**
